text: Castaffa Creek is a stream in the U.S. state of Mississippi. It is a tributary to Shubuta Creek. Castaffa is a name derived from the Choctaw language. Variant names are "Castaffy Creek" and "Chaslaffa Creek". ==References== Category:Rivers of Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of Clarke County, Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of Jasper County, Mississippi
title: Castaffa Creek
